{"type":"message","id":"0e62e412","parentId":"d773eb28","timestamp":"2026-03-13T13:59:56.373Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering command path issues**\n\nI need to provide a concise answer focusing on the installed CLI and the command path. It seems there might be a PATH issue, possibly requiring the user to restart their shell or OpenClaw. Since the user requested an action from the control-ui, I'll likely need to report back on the success of that action. This should help clarify things for them!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 装好了，只装了 **CLI**。\n\n现在机器上有两个相关命令：\n\n- `skillhub`：`/home/node/.local/bin/skillhub`\n- `clawhub`：`/home/node/.npm-global/bin/clawhub`（原来就有）\n\n我按你给的安装说明执行的是：\n\n```bash\ncurl -fsSL https://skillhub-1388575217.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/install/install.sh | bash -s -- --cli-only\n```\n\n### 当前状态\n`skillhub` 已安装成功，但**当前进程的 PATH 还没自动带上 `~/.local/bin`**，所以直接敲 `skillhub` 可能会提示找不到。\n\n临时可这样用：\n\n```bash\n~/.local/bin/skillhub --help\n```\n\n我已经验证过它能正常跑，看到的是 `search / install / upgrade / list / self-upgrade` 这些子命令。\n\n### 如果你想让系统里直接能敲 `skillhub`\n有两种办法：\n\n1. **重启 OpenClaw / 容器 / shell 进程**\n2. 或者把 `~/.local/bin` 加到 PATH\n\n如果你要，我下一步可以继续帮你做其中一种：\n- **帮你补 PATH**\n- **帮你验证 skillhub search/install**\n- **帮你把 OpenClaw 重启一下让它感知到新 CLI**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1239,"output":396,"cacheRead":19968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":21603,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773410386589}}
{"type":"message","id":"9c76c64e","parentId":"0e62e412","timestamp":"2026-03-13T14:07:52.902Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b5475edb090b0b2115cbdeb59edd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"sender\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Fri 2026-03-13 14:07 UTC\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\",\n  \"name\": \"ou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b5475edb090b0b2115cbdeb59edd]\nou_89d790689d0059dfcc29b83ffac2dab2: 把我能操作的范围限制到某个 compose 项目"}],"timestamp":1773410872895}}
{"type":"message","id":"f9fdb884","parentId":"9c76c64e","timestamp":"2026-03-13T14:08:36.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering conceptual answers**\n\nI’m thinking I need to provide a conceptual answer here, but I wonder if a memory search is necessary. It might relate to a prior decision, but it doesn’t seem mandatory; the current conversation context could suffice. I could explain how it works without delving into that. Also, I might offer insights about wrapper scripts and a note on the Docker socket, keeping it simple since no additional tools are required.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 可以，这个思路本身就是对的。\n\n你要的其实不是“让我会 Docker”，而是：\n\n> **我只能管某一个 compose 项目，别的容器、别的数据目录都碰不到。**\n\n不过先说一句实话：  \n**如果你直接把 docker.sock 给我，而且允许我随便跑 `docker` / `docker compose`，那“只限某个 compose 项目”这件事是靠约定，不是真限制。**  \n因为有了 daemon 权限，理论上还是能跳出去。\n\n所以要做到**真的限制范围**，推荐你用下面这套。\n\n---\n\n# 最稳的做法：白名单脚本 + 固定 compose 文件\n\n## 目标\n假设你只想让我管理这个项目：\n\n- compose 文件：`/opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml`\n\n我能做的只有：\n\n- 看状态\n- 看日志\n- 重启\n- 拉起\n- 停止\n\n我**不能**：\n\n- 管别的 compose 项目\n- 新建任意容器\n- 改挂载目录\n- 顺手去看别的业务数据\n\n---\n\n# 方案结构\n\n## 1）固定项目目录\n比如：\n\n```bash\n/opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml\n/srv/memos/config\n/srv/memos/data\n/srv/memos/uploads\n```\n\ncompose 文件里把挂载写死：\n\n```yaml\nservices:\n  memos:\n    image: neosmemo/memos:stable\n    container_name: memos\n    restart: unless-stopped\n    ports:\n      - \"5230:5230\"\n    volumes:\n      - /srv/memos/config:/var/opt/memos/config:ro\n      - /srv/memos/data:/var/opt/memos/data\n      - /srv/memos/uploads:/var/opt/memos/uploads\n```\n\n这里的关键是：\n- 项目位置固定\n- 数据目录固定\n- 配置目录尽量只读\n\n---\n\n## 2）宿主机只提供几个脚本\n例如：\n\n```bash\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-status\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-logs\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-restart\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-up\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-down\n```\n\n### `oc-memos-status`\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml ps\n```\n\n### `oc-memos-logs`\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml logs --tail=200\n```\n\n### `oc-memos-restart`\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml restart\n```\n\n### `oc-memos-up`\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml up -d\n```\n\n### `oc-memos-down`\n```bash\n#!/usr/bin/env bash\nset -euo pipefail\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml down\n```\n\n然后：\n\n```bash\nchmod 755 /usr/local/bin/oc-memos-*\n```\n\n---\n\n## 3）我只被允许调用这些脚本\n这样我操作时只走：\n\n- `oc-memos-status`\n- `oc-memos-logs`\n- `oc-memos-restart`\n\n而不是直接给我：\n\n- `docker`\n- `docker compose`\n- `docker run`\n\n这才是真正的范围限制。\n\n---\n\n# 为什么这比“直接让我用 compose”安全很多\n\n因为“只限某个 compose 项目”这件事，真正受控的是这几个东西：\n\n## 被固定住的\n- compose 文件路径\n- 项目名\n- 数据挂载目录\n- 允许执行的动作\n\n## 被禁止的\n- 临时换一个 compose 文件\n- 指向另一个目录\n- 新建附带任意挂载的容器\n- 顺手看别的服务日志或数据\n\n换句话说：\n\n> **限制的不是我的“意图”，而是我的“入口”。**\n\n---\n\n# 如果你还想再收紧一点\n\n## A. compose 文件权限只读\n比如：\n\n```bash\nchown root:root /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml\nchmod 644 /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml\n```\n\n这样我就算能执行脚本，也改不了 compose 内容。\n\n---\n\n## B. 脚本里禁止传参\n别写成这种：\n\n```bash\ndocker compose -f \"$1\" restart\n```\n\n要写死：\n\n```bash\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml restart\n```\n\n不接受外部输入，最稳。\n\n---\n\n## C. 日志脚本限制输出长度\n例如只看最近 200 行：\n\n```bash\ndocker compose -f /opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml logs --tail=200\n```\n\n别一口气把全量日志抡出来。\n\n---\n\n## D. 配置目录只读挂载\n比如：\n\n```yaml\n- /srv/memos/config:/var/opt/memos/config:ro\n```\n\n这样即便服务在跑，也少一层误写风险。\n\n---\n\n# 如果你是想让我“在 OpenClaw 里”这么工作\n那落地方式通常有两种。\n\n## 方式 1：我执行宿主机白名单脚本\n最干净。\n\n前提是：\n- OpenClaw 所在环境能调用宿主机这些脚本\n- 或者通过一个非常薄的代理来调用\n\n这适合你前面说的“让 Docker 里的我去管理别的容器”，但又不想把全套 Docker 权限交出来。\n\n---\n\n## 方式 2：做一个很薄的中间服务\n比如本机起一个小 API，只提供：\n\n- `/memos/status`\n- `/memos/logs`\n- `/memos/restart`\n\nAPI 背后实际调用固定脚本。  \n我只访问这个 API，不直接碰 Docker。\n\n### 好处\n- 权限边界更清楚\n- 以后扩展多个项目方便\n- 能加鉴权、审计、日志\n\n### 坏处\n- 比脚本多一层东西要维护\n\n---\n\n# 不太推荐的做法\n\n## “给 docker.sock，然后靠提示词要求我只管某个 compose”\n这个不叫限制，这叫**自觉**。  \n真要做权限边界，不能靠口头约定。\n\n## “给我 sudo + docker 命令，但让我别乱用”\n也不靠谱。  \n权限一旦给到位，范围就不是真的可控了。\n\n---\n\n# 你可以直接抄的最小方案\n\n## 项目\n```bash\n/opt/apps/memos/docker-compose.yml\n```\n\n## 脚本\n```bash\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-status\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-logs\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-restart\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-up\n/usr/local/bin/oc-memos-down\n```\n\n## 允许的能力\n- 状态\n- 日志\n- 重启\n- 启停\n\n## 不允许的能力\n- 任意 docker run\n- 任意 compose -f xxx\n- 改 compose\n- 管其它项目\n\n---\n\n# 一句话判断你有没有限制成功\n\n如果我还能自己决定下面任意一项，就说明**还没真限制住**：\n\n- compose 文件路径\n- 容器名\n- 挂载目录\n- 执行动作种类\n\n只要这些是我能改的，就不算“限制到某个 compose 项目”。\n\n---\n\n如果你愿意，我下一条可以直接给你一份**可落地模板**：\n\n1. 一个 `docker-compose.yml` 示例  \n2. 五个白名单脚本  \n3. 一个适合 OpenClaw 调用的最小接入方案  \n\n你回我一句：\n\n**“给我模板，项目名叫 xxx，compose 路径是 xxx”**\n\n我直接按你的实际路径写。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":19122,"output":1894,"cacheRead":1536,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22552,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773410872898}}
